snippet.title: Piczle Cross: Rune Factory teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Coming 2025, a celebration of the Rune Factory series in nonogram form! Capture monsters, fight bosses, customize your farm, find residents and a marriage partner. Select your weapon to prepare for battles with enemies. Enjoy it at your own pace or take on a difficult challenge.

https://www.piczlerunefactory.com
